Currently there is a remote api to getIssueCountForFilter(..) mirroring the getIssuesFromFilterWithLimit(..) api but there appears to be no counting analogue for the other search apis getIssuesFromJqlSearch(..), getIssuesFromTextSearchWithLimit(..), getIssuesFromTextSearchWithProject(..).  Please provide those analogues.

It's often useful to know the count of matching issues before retrieving the issues themselves, and occasionally the count is the only interesting thing anyway and having to retrieve the full list just to find the count is a crazy waste of processing power and bandwidth.
